NYF.short_name: iShares New York Muni Bond ETF
NYF.long_name: iShares New York Muni Bond ETF
NYF.summary:
The investment seeks to track the investment results of the S&P New York AMT-Free Municipal Bond IndexTM.
 The fund generally will invest at least 90% of its assets in the component securities of the underlying index and may invest up to 10% of its assets in certain futures, options and swap contracts, cash and cash equivalents. The index measures the performance of the investment-grade segment of the New York municipal bond market. The fund is non-diversified.
